The only difference between a bard and a rogue is: a rogue has better offense, can't wear plate, and has no mana bar and all it's armor is shades of black.  A bard is a rogue that can wear plate, can't backstab, can track, and has minimal chanter abilities, but like the ranger, paladin, and SK, it does get songs with effects that it's parent caster class, the enchanter, doesn't get like regen songs. <p><img src="http://members.home.net/cgoebel5/sig/Yshaasig.jpg"><br>Yshaa Dargonesti<br>
